  <script>
   function setCookie(name, value, days) {
            if (days) {
                var date = new Date();
                date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
                var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
            }
            else var expires = "";
            document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
        }

        function getCookie(name) {
            var nameEQ = name + "=";
            var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
            for (var i = 0; i &lt; ca.length; i++) {
                var c = ca[i];
                while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') c = c.substring(1, c.length);
                if (c.indexOf(nameEQ) == 0)
                    return c.substring(nameEQ.length, c.length);
            }
            return null;
        }

        function deleteCookie(name) {
            setCookie(name, "", -1);
        }
  </script>

  <script type="text/javascript">
   $(document).ready(function () {
            $(".dropdown img.flag").addClass("flagvisibility");

            $(".dropdown dt a").click(function () {
                $(".dropdown dd ul").toggle();
            });

            $(".dropdown dd ul li a").click(function () {
                var text = $(this).html();
                $(".dropdown dt a span").html(text);
                $(".dropdown dd ul").hide();
                $("#result").html("Selected value is: " + getSelectedValue("sample"));
            });

            function getSelectedValue(id) {
                return $("#" + id).find("dt a span.value").html();
            }

            $(document).bind('click', function (e) {
                var $clicked = $(e.target);
                if (!$clicked.parents().hasClass("dropdown"))
                    $(".dropdown dd ul").hide();
            });
        });

        $(document).ready(function () {
            $(".dropdown2 img.flag").addClass("flagvisibility");

            $(".dropdown2 dt a").click(function () {
                $(".dropdown2 dd ul").toggle();
            });

            $(".dropdown2 dd ul li a").click(function () {
                var text = $(this).html();
                $(".dropdown2 dt a span").html(text);
                $(".dropdown2 dd ul").hide();
                $("#result").html("Selected value is: " + getSelectedValue("sample2"));
            });

            $(document).bind('click', function (e) {
                var $clicked = $(e.target);

                    $(".dropdown2 dd ul").hide();
            });
        });

   $(function () {
            $("#divhiddens1 input[type=hidden]").each(function () {
                var z = "&lt;iframe id='ytplayer' type='text/html' width='482' height='390' src='" + $(this).val() + "' frameborder='0'/&gt;";
                $("#ulvideos").append("&lt;li&gt;" + z + "&lt;/li&gt;");
            });
            var po = document.createElement('script'); po.type = 'text/javascript'; po.async = true;
            po.src = 'https://apis.google.com/js/plusone.js?onload=onLoadCallback';
            var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(po, s);
            return false;

        });

        function onLoadCallback() {
            $("#divhiddens input[type=hidden]").each(function (n, m) {
                $("#ulsocial").append("&lt;li&gt;&lt;div id='widget-div" + n + "'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;");
            });
            $("#divhiddens input[type=hidden]").each(function (i, k) {
                gapi.post.render("widget-div" + i, { 'href': '' + $(this).val() + '' });
            });
        }

            function fsttime() {

                setTimeout(function () {
                    if (params !== "Enquiry.aspx") {
                        if (params !== "Onlinepayments.aspx") {
                            if (params !== "ICICI.aspx") {
                                if (params !== "atom.aspx") {
                                    if (params !== "rol.aspx") {
                                        if (params !== "NetBanking.aspx") {
                                            if (params !== "canadian-lawyer-seminar.aspx") {
                                                if (params !== "consultation-with-iccrc-member.aspx") {
                                                    if (params !== "visa-process.aspx") {
                                                        $("#divresume1").show();
                                                        $("#layerresume").css("height", $(document).height());
                                                        $("#divresume1").animate({ "margin-top": "2%" }, "800", "easeOutQuart");
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }, 30000);
            }
            function snd() {
                if ($("#divpopup").is(":visible") == false) {
                    setTimeout(function () {
                        if (params !== "Enquiry.aspx") {
                            if (params !== "Onlinepayments.aspx") {
                                if (params !== "ICICI.aspx") {
                                    if (params !== "atom.aspx") {
                                        if (params !== "rol.aspx") {
                                            if (params !== "NetBanking.aspx") {
                                                if (params !== "canadian-lawyer-seminar.aspx") {
                                                    if (params !== "consultation-with-iccrc-member.aspx") {
                                                        if (params !== "visa-process.aspx") {
                                                            $("#divresume1").show();
                                                            $("#layerresume").css("height", $(document).height());
                                                            $("#divresume1").animate({ "margin-top": "2%" }, "800", "easeOutQuart");
                                                            $("#divpopup").animate({ "bottom": "-45px" }, "slow", "linear");
                                                        }
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }

                    }, 120000);
                }
            }


            function thrd() {
                if ($("#divpopup").is(":visible") == false) {
                    setTimeout(function () {
                        if (params !== "Enquiry.aspx") {
                            if (params !== "Onlinepayments.aspx") {
                                if (params !== "ICICI.aspx") {
                                    if (params !== "atom.aspx") {
                                        if (params !== "NetBanking.aspx") {
                                            if (params !== "rol.aspx") {
                                                if (params !== "canadian-lawyer-seminar.aspx") {
                                                    if (params !== "consultation-with-iccrc-member.aspx") {
                                                        if (params !== "visa-process.aspx") {
                                                            $("#divresume1").show();
                                                            $("#layerresume").css("height", $(document).height());
                                                            $("#divresume1").animate({ "margin-top": "2%" }, "800", "easeOutQuart");
                                                            $("#divpopup").animate({ "bottom": "-45px" }, "slow", "linear");
                                                        }
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }, 240000);
                }
            }
            $(document).on("click", "#spanclose1", function () {

                $("#layerresume").css("height", "0px");
                $("#divresume1").animate({ "margin": "48% 0% 0 90%" }, "15000", "linear", function () {
                    $("#divresume1").css("margin", "-51% 33% 0% 33%");
                    $("#divpopup").css("display", "block");
                });
                $("#divpopup").animate({ "bottom": "0px" }, "slow", "linear", function () {
                    $("#divresume1").hide();
                });
            });

            $(document).on("click", "#maximizebutton", function () {
                $("#layerresume").css("height", $(document).height());
                $("#divresume1").css("margin", "48% 0% 0 90%");
                $("#divresume1").show();
                $("#divresume1").animate({ "margin": "2.1% 33%" }, "400", "easeOutCirc");
                $("#divpopup").animate({ "bottom": "-50px" }, "slow", "linear", function () {
                    $("#divpopup").css("display", "none");
                });
            });



            $(document).on("click", "#closebelowdiv", function () {
                time += 1;
                $("#divresume1").hide();
                if (time == 2) {
                    setCookie("cookie", "2", 10)
                    $("#divpopup").css("display", "none");
                    if ($("#divpopup").is(":visible") == false) {
                        snd();
                    }
                }
                if (time == 3) {
                    setCookie("cookie", "3", 10)
                    $("#divpopup").css("display", "none");
                    if ($("#divpopup").is(":visible") == false) {
                        thrd();
                    }
                }
                $("#divpopup").css("display", "none");

            });

        });

               <div class="quick_enquiry3">
                <script type="text/javascript">
                 $(function () {
         $("#btnsub").click(function () {

             if ($('#' + 'ContentPlaceHolder1_ndpagecontrols_me1_txtLivingCountry').val().length == 0) {
                 $("#errorMsg").text("Pls fill Living Country fields above.");
                 return false;
             }
             if ($('#' + 'ContentPlaceHolder1_ndpagecontrols_me1_txtWanttogo').val().length == 0) {
                 $("#errorMsg").text("Pls fill Where You want to go fields above.");
                 return false;
             }

                                            <div class="h3r">
                                             Why you should hire a visa consultant wh...
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="post-content">
                                             <img class="left" id="thPage1_ArticleRepeater_Image1_0" src="https://www.immigrationoverseas.com//NewsImages/123456.jpg" style="height:72px;width:132px;"/>
                                             <p class="Standard" style="text-align: justify;">
                                              <span style="font-family: Arial;">
                                               In recent times, the immigration movement has been phenomenal specially from, under developed countries to the develo
                                               <a href="digital-media/article/why-you-should-hire-a-visa-consultant-while-applying-for-a-visa-25.aspx" id="thPage1_ArticleRepeater_HyperLink1_0">
                                                Read More..
                                               </a>
                                              </span>
                                             </p>
                                            </div>
                                           </div>
                                          </div>
                                         </div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                         <div class="contents">
                                          <div class="post">
                                           <div class="entry">
                                            <div class="h3r">
                                             How to get Australian citizenship?...
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="post-content">
                                             <img class="left" id="thPage1_ArticleRepeater_Image1_1" src="https://www.immigrationoverseas.com//NewsImages/Get-Visa-For-Australia-Immigration.jpg" style="height:72px;width:132px;"/>
